    "title": "史を顧みて",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "借りた資料を返却しに図書室を訪れると――",
            "enText": "When I visited the library to \nreturn borrowed materials―",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "pathId": -1229806351137284826,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "――あら。\r\nトレーナーさんも図書室に御用ですか？",
            "enText": "―Oh, my. Is your trainer here \nfor the library, too?",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ああ、アルダンも？",
                    "enText": "Oh, and Aldan?",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "うん、アルダンも？",
                    "enText": "Yeah, and Aldan?",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": -603615076979206489
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -2495291849957936614
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8794305260929922126,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "歴史書を読みに参りました。\r\n実はここの図書室、密かにその方面の\n蔵書が充実していまして……。",
            "enText": "I came here to read a history book. In fact, \nthe library here is secretly well-stocked \nwith books in that field. ……",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -165722004913180297
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": -9028605449901316494
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7901797981448563122,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "空いた時間にはよくこうして、\r\n活用させてもらっているのです。",
            "enText": "I often take advantage of \nmy free time in this way.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "歴史書、好きなんだな",
                    "enText": "History books, you like them.",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "歴史書、好きなんだね",
                    "enText": "History books, you like them.",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": 6155847127313704118
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 6227604744960260149
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6152305199266146362,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "はい。\r\n……とても心惹かれます。",
            "enText": "Yes, I am very interested in this. I am very \nfascinated by ……",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": 7598691208814000166
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -8959140127618449437
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 451612559638880699,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "過去の人々の営みが書となり、“今”を\r\n生きる私たちにまで永く残されている……。\nその事実だけで心震えるものがあり――",
            "enText": "The work of people in the past has become a \nbook, and has been preserved for us who live \nin the \"present\".…… That fact alone is enough \nto make one's heart tremble.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 2956064270559629816
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": 4937691410087125388
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": 1492654198373282659
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1348290349531297820,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "内容に触れ、当時を生きる人々や、\r\n記述した歴史家の情動に想いを馳せることで、\n私の中の世界が広がっていく感動もあります。",
            "enText": "I am touched by the contents of the book, and \nby thinking about the emotions of the people \nwho lived in those days and the historians \nwho wrote about them. I am moved by the way \nmy world expands.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 124,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 7643301340745785119
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 90,
                    "pathId": -5290941374353008348
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 135,
                    "pathId": 2892613162400482818
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7027244804961251410,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "読むたびに、私もこの世界において\r\nかく真摯にありたいと感じ――",
            "enText": "Every time I read it, I feel like I want to \nbe as sincere as possible in this world.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": 1406323661549924063
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -7093662035284285359
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7921479234027911655,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "自分の“今”を全うする上で必要な……\r\n勇気に近いものをいただけるのです。",
            "enText": "It gives me something close to the…… courage \nI need to fulfill my \"now\".",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": 4627851511084957211
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 6530654530147476865
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -219751004326395627,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "どこか楽し気に話すメジロアルダン。\r\nその様子を見て自分も、彼女の言う感覚に\n触れてみたいと思い――",
            "enText": "Mejiro Aldan speaks somewhat happily. I was \nalso interested in the sensation that she was \ntalking about. I wanted to touch―",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "俺も、歴史書を何か読んでみたいな",
                    "enText": "I, too, would love to read something \nfrom a history book.",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "私も、歴史書を何か読んでみたいな",
                    "enText": "I, too, would love to read something \nfrom a history book.",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 6687336307096992417
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 5592434381527582145
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7086791793298492854,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "まあ……！\r\n本当ですか？",
            "enText": "Well, ……! Really?",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 42,
                    "pathId": -8246706106864705163
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": 3905707263943172874
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7158366533995765832,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "あの、それでしたら……\r\nよろしければなのですが――",
            "enText": "Well, I'm…… if you don't mind…",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": -8593524339638904215
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -4293481446130755942
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5435756613615427932,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "トレーナーさんが読まれる本を探すのに、\r\nお手伝いさせていただけないでしょうか。",
            "enText": "I would like to help the trainer \nfind books to read.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いいのか？",
                    "enText": "Are you sure?",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "いいの？",
                    "enText": "Are you sure?",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -806311521256569159
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -5249477778441848115
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -5352170614851946584
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -431053352809713926,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "はい、ぜひ！",
            "enText": "Yes, by all means!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 52,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -6725859197914646180
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -4658014818625871449
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": 1798666304876160368
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5954766777106916824,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "たとえば、『このような感じの歴史書を\r\n読んでみたい』といった要望はありますか？\n私の知る限りでお薦めできればと思います。",
            "enText": "Do you have any requests, for example, 'I \nwould like to read a history book that feels \nlike this one'? I would be happy to make \nrecommendations to the best of my knowledge.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 124,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": -4924526194934904409
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 135,
                    "pathId": 8616088906252034792
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9078000936153622528,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "きっとメジロアルダンならば、たくさんの\r\n歴史書を知っているはずだ。ここはお言葉に\n甘えてオススメを聞くのがいいだろう。",
            "enText": "Surely Mejiro Aldan would know a lot of \nhistory books. I'll take your word for it \nhere. I would be happy to take your word for \nit and ask for your recommendation.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 134,
                    "pathId": 6300854720435812757
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 134,
                    "pathId": 6340849407459591481
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7709952094566242333,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "歴史書を読むとするならば――",
            "enText": "If I were to read a history book―",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "波乱万丈なものが読みたい",
                    "enText": "I want to read something tumultuous.",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "初心者向けのものが読みたい",
                    "enText": "I want to read something for beginners.",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "アルダンのお気に入りが読みたい",
                    "enText": "I'd love to read Aldan's favorites.",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -8246240924007140466
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -6859381797794626097
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 500402551944486957,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "波乱万丈……となると、\r\n国家などの興亡を取り扱ったものが\n希望に沿うかもしれませんね。",
            "enText": "If you are looking for a tumultuous…… \nsomething that deals with the rise and fall \nof nations, etc. might be in line with what \nyou are hoping for.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": -2316301061727057072
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 113,
                    "pathId": 2917860357156199723
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2656633072095800722,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "属する共同体の存亡に直面した人々の、\r\nひとつひとつの選択が重なって歴史を変える\n大きなうねりとなる様は、正に波乱――",
            "enText": "The choices made by people faced with the \nexistence or destruction of their community \nwill combine to change history. The way in \nwhich the choices made by people facing the \nfate of the community to which they belong \ncombine to form a great swell that changes \nhistory is truly tumultuous.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 98,
                    "pathId": 5361810757978370861
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": 4948973991686427896
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3671748701826849271,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "いくつか思いついた候補があります。\r\nさっそく見てみましょうか。",
            "enText": "There are a few candidates I have \ncome up with. Let's take a look \nat them right away, shall we?",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -987277879983738206
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -4834634988874158983
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2050192656769877007,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その後、メジロアルダンに\r\nオススメを見繕ってもらい――",
            "enText": "After that, I had Mejiro Aldan make some \nrecommendations for me.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": -1141749904678543047
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": 5628132011522660343
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3975947999208284852,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "メジロアルダンの言葉を思い出しながら\r\n読むことで、彼女の大事にしているものに\n触れられたような気がしたのだった……。",
            "enText": "Reading Mejiro Aldan's words as I remembered \nthem, I felt as if I had been in touch \nwith what she cherished. I felt as if \nI had been touched. ……",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "pathId": 7430496398663617420,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "初心者向け……となると、\r\n特定の人物の歴史を取り扱ったものが\n希望に沿うかもしれませんね。",
            "enText": "For a beginner…… something dealing \nwith the history of a specific person \nmight be what you want.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 94,
                    "pathId": -5232236076823482535
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": 1384501721287731714
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6204574461066010340,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "小説における、登場人物を介し\r\n物語に触れるかのように、その人の生涯を\n介し歴史に触れられるので――",
            "enText": "In a novel, you can touch a person's life and \nhistory as if you were touching a story \nthrough a character. history through a \ncharacter in a novel, as if you were touching \na story through a character in a novel.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": -6213796926363540536
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 8453975805160063588
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -602054378845223082,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "いくつか思いついた候補があります。\r\nさっそく見てみましょうか。",
            "enText": "There are a few candidates I have \ncome up with. Let's take a look \nat them right away, shall we?",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -8688718308153793738
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -7945011160878653402
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1703219956233829121,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その後、メジロアルダンに\r\nオススメを見繕ってもらい――",
            "enText": "After that, I had Mejiro Aldan make some \nrecommendations for me.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": -3000901351682871054
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": -5681124670650592003
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5005414947334620388,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "メジロアルダンの言葉を思い出しながら\r\n読むことで、彼女の大事にしているものに\n触れられたような気がしたのだった……。",
            "enText": "Reading Mejiro Aldan's words as I remembered \nthem, I felt as if I had been in touch \nwith what she cherished. I felt as if \nI had been touched. ……",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "pathId": 9154070063161631599,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "私のお気に入り……！\r\nそれはもちろん構わないのですが――",
            "enText": "My favorite ……! That's fine, \nof course―but―I'm not sure what \nyou're talking about.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 47,
                    "pathId": -5370406071233220091
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -8513502148015218483
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6932673279240828028,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "…………どうしましょう。",
            "enText": "……… What should we do?",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どうかした？",
                    "enText": "What's wrong?",
                    "nextBlock": 30
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "どうかしたの？",
                    "enText": "What's wrong?",
                    "nextBlock": 30
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 32,
                    "pathId": -6007054496883272441
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -8643114745333731844
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5077220690669980500,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "お恥ずかしい話なのですが、その……\r\nお気に入りが多すぎて……\nなかなかひとつに、絞り切れないのです。",
            "enText": "I'm embarrassed to say that I have so many…… \nfavorites that I can't narrow it down to just \none…… I can't narrow it down to just one.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": -3274275705658359189
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 5871693569842972642
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1291713111240737189,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロアルダン",
            "enName": "Mejiro Ardan",
            "jpText": "それに、こうして誰かに\r\n歴史書をお薦めする機会も、\nこれまで少なかったので……――",
            "enText": "And I have not had many opportunities \nto recommend history books to others \nin this way. ……―",
